Package org.neo4j.bolt.v3.messaging.decoder

Class PrimitiveOnlyValueWriter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.neo4j.kernel.impl.util.BaseToObjectValueWriter<RuntimeException>
      • org.neo4j.bolt.v3.messaging.decoder.PrimitiveOnlyValueWriter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AnyValueWriter<RuntimeException>, ValueWriter<RuntimeException>
    public class PrimitiveOnlyValueWriter
extends BaseToObjectValueWriter<RuntimeException>
    Writer that allows to convert AnyValue to any primitive Java type. It explicitly prohibits conversion of nodes, relationships, spatial and temporal types. They are not expected in auth token map.
